<p>
<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>workaround: for all x<0, valley elevation at x=0 (until we have a model for x<0 that matches background images and works with tools)
<li>fix: constrain right pan arrow the same as dragging the bear
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>background image is so large that it exceeds JVM heap space and causes OutOfMemoryException
<li>model of valley floor doesn't match background image for x<0
<li>"Steady State" button doesn't advance clock time
<li>glacier starts up in steady state, but with no debris or ripple in the ice, and no moraine
<li>registration points (small red circles and blue dots) are shown in the background image
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>snowfall is not visible
<li>Experiments tab
<li>English/metric units control
<li>time-based graphs
<li>Save/Load
<li>Help
</ul>
